==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Papillate
<hw>Pap"il*late</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t. & i.</pos> <def>To cover
with papill⟦ae⟧; to take the form of a papilla, or of
papill⟦ae⟧.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Papillate</ent>⟦br⟧

